info.text: Once applied to your Amazon account, the entire amount will be added to your gift card balance. Your gift card balance will be applied automatically to eligible orders during the checkout process and when using 1-Click. If you don't want to use your gift card balance on your order, you can unselect it as a payment method in checkout.
Need to redeem a gift card?
For plastic gift cards, you may need to scratch off the coating on the back of the card to reveal the claim code. The claim code isn't the 16-digit card number.
Apply a Gift Card to Your Account
